		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:1:1:N"/>
		<identifier rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">N</identifier>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">N</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">Tally Magiczl</fullTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
  <p>In the future, a boy studies science in a magical age where it is popularly considered irrelevant.</p>
  <p>Pretty much exclusively a spinoff (and inversion) of <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/1/1/2003-09/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::1:1:2003-09"><code>bjmns:1:1:2003-09</code></a>, and not earlier concepts.</p>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
