		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">The Legend of Zelda: A Missing Link</fullTitle>
		<abbreviatedTitle xml:lang="en">A Missing Link</abbreviatedTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>Originally written for a writing competition among friends I was trying to make happen but never did.  The original file was a ClarisWorks document; the provided plaintext was extracted by opening it in an ordinary text editor.</p>
</div></contents>
