		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">The Legend of Ilia: Iota</fullTitle>
		<abbreviatedTitle xml:lang="en">Iota</abbreviatedTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>I <em>quite liked</em> the beginning of this story, and re·used it <em>often</em>.  Unfortunately, I could never decide on a place for the story to go from there.</p>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
