	<Volume rdf:about="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::6:Λ">
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="./6/Λ/"/>
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:6:Λ"/>
		<identifier rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">Epona</identifier>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">Λ</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">Epona</fullTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>A (planned) <em>prequel</em> to <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/6/Ι/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::6:Ι"><code>bjmns:6:Ι</code></a> and also <a href="http://id.loc.gov/resources/hubs/4a3df29ff3a489e191b1df29386dd28b"><code>lcbh:4a3df29ff3a489e191b1df29386dd28b</code></a> by extension.  It never made it very far mostly because I couldn’t come up with any good plot starring children.</p>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
