	<p>A (planned) direct sequel to <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/6/Ι/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::6:Ι"><code>bjmns:6:Ι</code></a>, because I really liked that story, even though I never got very far with either.</p>
</div></contents>
