	</Version>
		</includes>
		<includes>
	<Version rdf:about="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::7:1:Forces">
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="./7/1/Forces/"/>
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:7:1:Forces"/>
		<identifier rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">Forces</identifier>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">Forces</index>
		<inspiration rdf:resource="http://id.loc.gov/resources/hubs/86c4fe6afa05691fd8b3de265be0f78f"/>
		<inspiration rdf:resource="http://id.loc.gov/resources/hubs/e3909dca25ea3cccbbd1f95567ce8dff"/>
		<inspiration rdf:resource="http://id.loc.gov/resources/works/14075923"/>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>This is almost a direct reworking of the plotline in the back half of <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/6/Α/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::6:Α"><code>bjmns:6:Α</code></a>, which I (later) spoofed lightly in <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/6/NintendoRealm/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::6:NintendoRealm"><code>bjmns:6:NintendoRealm</code></a>.  The emphasis on Light/Dark Worlds is taken from <a href="http://id.loc.gov/resources/hubs/86c4fe6afa05691fd8b3de265be0f78f"><code>lcbh:86c4fe6afa05691fd8b3de265be0f78f</code></a> and the Twilight Realm concept draws influence from not only <a href="http://id.loc.gov/resources/hubs/4a3df29ff3a489e191b1df29386dd28b"><code>lcbh:4a3df29ff3a489e191b1df29386dd28b</code></a> but also <a href="http://id.loc.gov/resources/hubs/e3909dca25ea3cccbbd1f95567ce8dff"><code>lcbh:e3909dca25ea3cccbbd1f95567ce8dff</code></a> and possibly <a href="http://id.loc.gov/resources/works/14075923"><code>lcbw:14075923</code></a> as well.</p>
	<p>See <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/7/1/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::7:1"><code>bjmns:7:1</code></a> for a later attempt at this same idea.</p>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
